targets.rawSql: SELECT COALESCE(AVG(confidence), 0.0) * 100 as value FROM ml_predictions WHERE $__timeFilter(timestamp) AND namespace NOT IN ('kube-system', 'kube-public', 'kube-node-lease', 'local-path-storage')
SELECT 0.0 as value
SELECT COALESCE(COUNT(*)::float / GREATEST(EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM (MAX(timestamp) - MIN(timestamp))), 1), 0.0) as value FROM ml_predictions WHERE $__timeFilter(timestamp)
SELECT 'ensemble' as value
SELECT COALESCE(COUNT(*), 0) as value FROM ml_predictions WHERE $__timeFilter(timestamp)
SELECT 0.0 as value

SELECT
  time_bucket('1 minute', timestamp) as time,
  COALESCE(COUNT(*), 0) as value
FROM ml_predictions
WHERE $__timeFilter(timestamp)
GROUP BY time
ORDER BY time
